songs.title: Blunt Ta My Lips
songs.lyrics:

Gun on my hip (hip)
Guap do frontflips (flip)
Pocket got blue dip (dip)

Bitch ain’t from here (here)
Engine in the rear (rear)
Codeine and root beer (beer)
